Package stocker.model.stockdata

Class StockData

  • java.lang.Object
    • stocker.model.stockdata.StockData
  • public class StockData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains various data about a particular stock. Search query data StockDataSearch, data from the quote query StockDataQuote, real-time data, historical data and the data calculated from it. The "calculated data" as well as the historical data StockDataHistoric are always related to a certain time interval (TimeInterval), so an allocation table for data management is ideal. Real-time data StockDataRealtime is kept as a list. Various getter methods for querying the pull data create a new "dummy" object with the data access status StockDataStateType.unclear. getStockDataHistoric(TimeInterval), getStockDataQuote() and getStockDataSearch()
    Author:
    Christoph Kaplan
